        <div class="icon">🏔️</div>
        <strong>My Territory</strong>
        <p>Colorado Springs<br>Woodland Park<br>Denver & the Rockies</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <blockquote class="about-quote">
      "My kids are my driving force - they inspire me to persevere and give my best in everything I do."
