      </div>
      <div class="tip-card">
        <div class="t-icon">⭐</div>
        <h3>Ratings Matter</h3>
        <p>I take pride in every ride. A 5-star rating means the world to me.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:1.5rem; padding:1rem 1.2rem; background:var(--cream); border-radius:1rem; font-size:0.88rem; color:var(--stone);">
      <strong style="color:var(--pine);">📋 Colorado Child Seat Law</strong><br>
